Brockman Says Wayne Richards Has Resigned as Managing Director

-- B y   V i c t o r i a   B a t c h e l o r
-- 
2011-09-18T22:32:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-18/brockman-says-wayne-richards-has-resigned-as-managing-director.html
Brockman Resources Ltd. (BRM)  said Wayne
Richards has resigned as managing director on mutually agreed
terms and Colin Paterson has been appointed interim chief
executive officer, according to a regulatory filing. Barry
Cusack has resigned as chairman and Peter Luk has been
appointed a non-executive director and chairman, the company
said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Victoria Batchelor at 
 vbatchelor@bloomberg.net  